Independently implemented multi-provider image generation MCP.
Architecture inspired by:
  - wind-cn-mcp / cn-academic-search-mcp (this repo's existing multi-provider MCPs)

Image model integrations use public APIs/SDKs:
  - DALL-E 3: OpenAI public API (https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/images)
  - FLUX.1: Replicate / fal.ai public APIs
  - Imagen 3: Google Vertex AI public docs
  - Ideogram v2: Replicate public API
  - Recraft v3: Replicate public API

No source code copied. Image generation requires user-provided API keys.
Users must comply with each model provider's terms of service.
